                "updated_time": 1559028727,
                "content": "<p>先来看看联邦快递是家什么公司，根据维基百科记载，它是一家国际性<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//wc.yooooo.us/wiki/%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E9%2581%259E%2522%2520%255Co%2520%2522%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E9%2580%2592\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">快递</a>集团，提供隔夜快递、地面快递、重型货物运送、文件<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//wc.yooooo.us/wiki/%25E5%25A4%258D%25E5%258D%25B0%2522%2520%255Co%2520%2522%25E5%25A4%258D%25E5%258D%25B0\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">复印</a>及<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//wc.yooooo.us/wiki/%25E7%2589%25A9%25E6%25B5%2581%2522%2520%255Co%2520%2522%25E7%2589%25A9%25E6%25B5%2581\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">物流</a>服务，总部设于<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//wc.yooooo.us/wiki/%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%2522%2520%255Co%2520%2522%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259B%25BD\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">美国</a><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//wc.yooooo.us/wiki/%25E7%2594%25B0%25E7%25B4%258D%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E5%25B7%259E%2522%2520%255Co%2520%2522%25E7%2594%25B0%25E7%25BA%25B3%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E5%25B7%259E\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">田纳西州</a>，是目前世界最大的快递运输公司之一。</p><p>其诞生于1971年，由前<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//wc.yooooo.us/wiki/%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E8%25BB%258D%25E9%2599%25B8%25E6%2588%25B0%25E9%259A%258A%2522%2520%255Co%2520%2522%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259B%25BD%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E5%2586%259B%25E9%2599%2586%25E6%2588%2598%25E9%2598%259F\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">美国海军陆战队</a>员Frederick W. Smith在<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//wc.yooooo.us/wiki/%25E9%2598%25BF%25E8%2582%25AF%25E8%2589%25B2%25E5%25B7%259E%2522%2520%255Co%2520%2522%25E9%2598%25BF%25E8%2582%25AF%25E8%2589%25B2%25E5%25B7%259E\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">阿肯色州</a><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//wc.yooooo.us/wiki/%25E5%25B0%258F%25E7%259F%25B3%25E5%259F%258E%2522%2520%255Co%2520%2522%25E5%25B0%258F%25E7%259F%25B3%25E5%259F%258E\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">小石城</a>创立。</p><p>EMMMM，如果我国也有个美利坚式的国土安全局，一定会把这家企业圈进“安全隐患”的范畴里，毕竟创始人有别国军队背景~</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-4572dc0c5c4eb279761f1ab06dbf0700_b.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"439\" data-rawheight=\"348\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"439\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-4572dc0c5c4eb279761f1ab06dbf0700_r.jpg\"></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='439'%20height='348'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"439\" data-rawheight=\"348\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"439\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-4572dc0c5c4eb279761f1ab06dbf0700_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-4572dc0c5c4eb279761f1ab06dbf0700_b.jpg\"></figure><p><br></p><p>不过中国是开放市场，不像某些灯塔那样嘴上一套背地一套，审查比谁都严格，所以联邦快递在华的运营未受影响，甚至不少大型企业客户都选择了它。</p><p>然而，信任没有获得对等的信任。</p><p>华为周五对路透社表示，联邦快递（FedEx）近期将从日本寄往中国华为的两件包裹寄到了美国，并试图将另外两件从越南寄往华为亚洲其他地区办事处的包裹也转运到美国，这些行为都是未经授权的。</p><p>作为证据，华为还提供了联邦快递追踪记录的图像。</p><p>这就完全是不要碧莲了，亏它23号还出官方声明辟谣，说没这回事，结果被正主直接打脸。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-3f99cb09856221826e863208608fd190_b.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"510\" data-rawheight=\"649\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"510\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-3f99cb09856221826e863208608fd190_r.jpg\"></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='510'%20height='649'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"510\" data-rawheight=\"649\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"510\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-3f99cb09856221826e863208608fd190_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-3f99cb09856221826e863208608fd190_b.jpg\"></figure><p><br></p><p>我们不说别的，单是这种做法就违背了一个递送行业最基本的准则，你是美国企业不假，但你得先是一家做递送的美国企业，而且还是个国际性的集团公司，无视职责道德和商业信誉，让人们看清了到底是谁才可以操控本国的企业，是谁才能将本国企业当做武器去进攻别的国家。</p><p>再往美国最喜欢提的“国家安全”方面说，联邦快递这种做法就是实打实地威胁我国邮政安全，放在战时这就是敌对行为，负责人抓起来枪毙都没问题。</p><p>说句实话，自从特朗普政府开始对付华为起，世界人民对于美国的认知就一再被刷新下限，而在我国，公知多年用谎言辛苦编织的“自由灯塔”幻象，也被特朗普自己一把戳破。</p><p>什么自由贸易，什么平等交往，什么国际道义，什么契约精神，通通都是骗鬼的话。</p><p>如今，美国政府无所不用其极，以全方位、超限战的思维打击中国和中国企业，还凭舆论优势倒打一耙，栽赃我国企业配合政府作恶，其实只是印证了一句话而已：</p><p><b>一束光照进灯塔，灯塔里的肮脏龌龊被显现。于是，这束光便有了罪。</b></p><p></p><p></p>",
